sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Electron App
    participant DB as database.cjs
    participant IPC as ipc.cjs
    participant MCM as McpClientManager
    participant MCP as MCP Server Process
    participant LLM as LLM API
    participant UI as Renderer (Home)

    Note over App,UI: === 流程1: 应用启动 → MCP 自动连接 ===

    App->>IPC: app.whenReady()
    IPC->>DB: 初始化数据库
    IPC->>MCM: initialize(mainWindow)
    MCM->>DB: SELECT * FROM mcp_servers WHERE enabled=1
    DB-->>MCM: enabledServers[]

    loop 每个启用的 server
        MCM->>MCM: connectServer(config)
        MCM->>MCM: pushStatus → "connecting"
        MCM->>MCP: spawn(command, args) → StdioClientTransport
        MCM->>MCP: client.connect(transport) [timeout:10s]
        alt 连接成功
            MCM->>MCP: client.request("tools/list")
            MCP-->>MCM: tools[]
            MCM->>MCM: cache tools, set status "connected"
            MCM->>MCM: pushStatus + pushTools
        else 连接失败/超时
            MCM->>MCM: set status "error", pushStatus
            MCM->>MCM: scheduleReconnect(serverId)
        end
    end

    Note over App,UI: === 流程2: 配置热更新 → 自动重连 ===

    UI->>IPC: mcp:update (enabled toggle)
    IPC->>DB: UPDATE mcp_servers
    DB-->>IPC: updated config
    IPC->>MCM: onServerConfigChanged({type:"update"})

    alt enabled: false→true 或 command/args变更
        MCM->>MCM: disconnectServer → connectServer
        MCM-->>UI: pushStatus + pushTools
    else enabled: true→false
        MCM->>MCM: disconnectServer + clearReconnect
        MCM-->>UI: pushStatus → "disconnected"
    end

    Note over App,UI: === 流程3: LLM 工具注入与调用循环 ===

    UI->>IPC: chatWithAI(messages, options)
    IPC->>MCM: getAllToolsForLLM("openai")
    MCM-->>IPC: ToolDefinition[] (serverName__toolName)

    loop 工具调用循环 (round=0..4, max=5)
        IPC->>LLM: _callModel(messages, {tools, tool_choice:"auto"})
        LLM-->>IPC: response

        alt response.tool_calls 存在 且 round < 5
            IPC->>IPC: round++
            loop 每个 tool_call
                IPC->>IPC: parseToolName → {serverName, toolName}
                IPC->>MCM: executeTool(serverId, toolName, args)
                MCM->>MCP: client.callTool(toolName, args)
                MCP-->>MCM: result
                MCM-->>IPC: ToolCallResult
                IPC->>IPC: messages.push(tool_result)
                IPC-->>UI: chat:tool-progress
            end
        else 无 tool_calls 或 round >= 5
            IPC-->>UI: 最终文本响应
        end
    end

    Note over App,UI: === 流程4: 断线重连 (P1) ===

    MCP-->>MCM: 进程意外退出 (close event)
    MCM->>MCM: set status "error", pushStatus
    MCM->>MCM: scheduleReconnect(serverId)

    loop 指数退避 (1s→2s→4s→8s→...→max30s)
        MCM->>MCM: wait(delay)
        MCM->>MCP: spawn + connect [timeout:10s]
        alt 重连成功
            MCM->>MCP: tools/list
            MCM->>MCM: clearReconnect, pushStatus "connected"
        else 重连失败
            MCM->>MCM: delay = min(delay*2, 30000)
            MCM->>MCM: pushStatus "error"
        end
    end
